{"tid":1316653,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［真相-震驚七百萬人］14/7 新城市廣場內..","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T01:24:16.000Z","uid":42487,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"236e562e29a7c5a83734aa61f635cda7223d79a8","tid":1316653,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"有人形跡可疑、形單隻影、兇神惡煞地追趕市民<br />\n與警隊人員「守護市民」形象完全不符<br />\n同時穿著警隊衣服，但身上並無佩帶委任證及展示其警員號碼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重懷疑高度危險人物「冒警」人士</span><br />\n<br />\n為保護香港市民<br />\n幾位英勇市民合力制止其惡行<br />\n希望能夠將其繩之於法<br />\n<br />\n有見<span style=\"color: red;\">冒警情況乃非常危險</span><br />\n為了以免引人誤會及易於分辦，特此呼籲警方執行任務時必須 佩帶及出示委任證及警員編號<br />\n以免產生任何不必要誤會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vfS3KbB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvfS3KbB.png&h=118274b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nP.s 此圖為中國內地出售警員背心"},{"pid":"3cab53fee998197b1caeaf9be0df1be0254aa529","tid":1316653,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c4a8f0aafed30b462a478d108e7aeb28bb916f7","tid":1316653,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bebb355964c8ce9d2af0aa6af08fcfc5d09bf2cd","tid":1316653,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAN7rrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAN7rrO.jpg&h=25a07d9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75e4206a12043606c9a8102586575a6336a081fb","tid":1316653,"uid":105485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72d4712a2817973c598f3f08cf1763e6c51f1059","tid":1316653,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bebb355964c8ce9d2af0aa6af08fcfc5d09bf2cd","tid":1316653,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07